modName: Whitewind Cabin - Player Home - OLD VERSION
summary:
Whitewind is a Medium Sized Cabin that\'s covered in snow & sits way out in Solitary Lands. It\'s Located just beyond Windhelm, on-top of snowy hills, which are constantly assaulted by blizzards and snowstorms.

With its temperatures fallen below Zero, it\'s the perfect location for a True Nord.
descriptionHtml:
NOTE: This Home may not be perfect, but keep in mind that this IS the first mod I\'ve ever created!

Rate, comment and enjoy.

Peace, xXxSyNc08.
